Former Fugees member Pras Michel on trial for alleged multimillion-dollar politics conspiracy
Former Fugees member Pras Michel is on trial for allegations of money laundering, campaign-finance violations and other charges. Celebrity lawyer and Emory University trial law professor Randy Kessler discusses the case with CBS News' Anne-Marie Green and Vlad Duthiers.
